Police in Nakuru have arrested a 45-year-old man who was accused of showing pornographic videos to school going children. Thomas Musabili who was arrested by police officers in his home in station area in Nakuru West had been accused of molesting and showing sexual related movies to boys between the age of 9 and 10 years. Confirming the incident, Nakuru OCPD Joshua Omukata during an interview with Standard said that his officers conducted the operation after they received a tip off from members of the public who noticed school going children who start flowing into the man&#39;s house at around 3pm daily. &quot;We received a report from the members of the public that one suspects was showing pornographic videos to young children and we immediately embarked on an investigation that led to his arrest,&quot; said Omukata.&nbsp;